'''Glowball''' was a [[Force power/Legends|Force technique]] invented by the [[Arcona/Legends|Arcona]] [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Izal Waz]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

To create a glowball, Waz would use [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] to gather ambient light into one location. The resulting phenomenon resembled a small [[Star/Legends|star]] and could be used to hide ships in battle from the enemy. Early utilizations of the glowball completely drained Waz of his energy, causing physical collapse.

The first documented usage occurred at [[Arkania/Legends|Arkania]], where Waz hid the blastboat ''[[Jolly Man]]'' from the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] in an attempt to capture a [[yammosk]].

The technique was later adopted by [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] and other [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], as well.

